reviewText: Good twists to the story.  Paul McGann!

Intriguing story line but sometimes difficult to follow the dialogue. The title made more sense after they played the game. Spooky in parts but ended well. Lots of plot twists to try to follow. OK but other series I've seen are better.
Kaz, played by Brendan Coyle, is a deep thoughtful soul. Fifty shades of loyalty!!! Will watch it over and over again!!!
I love this show. It was very well done. Brendan coyle did a wonderful job. I loved the way you are kept in suspense.
